0.1.0-beta.1 (March 11, 2026)
- Added gateway-driven alert banner system for settings and room views.
- Decoupled alert rendering from a specific sidecar by using a generic sidecar alert provider contract.
- Improved sidecar integration (ordered plugin behavior and presentation title resolution).
- Included multiple stability and quality fixes (guest lobby/group assignment, approvalbeforejoin, code quality).
